title: MisterMusic Show 348 indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 348 [120 minutes]  192 kbps MP3 stereo-



MisterMusic is back with new music from Built To Spill, Wolf Alice, My Double My Brother, and Aero Flynn. 
Plus a number one modern rock hit from 1989 is the 'Oldie of the Week'. A song that
topped the US chart in early April that year.
It's  two hours of indie, alternative and classic hits from over 5 decades of rock.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
